# Project Structure and Navigation

## Monorepo Overview

This is a Next.js monorepo powered by Turborepo. Navigate to specific parts using these references:

### Applications

- [apps/web](mdc:apps/web) - Personal website with blog, projects, and interactive features
- [apps/docs](mdc:apps/docs) - Component documentation site with demos

### Core Packages

- [packages/db](mdc:packages/db) - Database layer with Drizzle ORM schemas
- [packages/ui](mdc:packages/ui) - Shared component library
- [packages/i18n](mdc:packages/i18n) - Internationalization (en, zh-CN, zh-TW)
- [packages/env](mdc:packages/env) - Type-safe environment variables

### Development Tools

- [packages/eslint-config](mdc:packages/eslint-config) - ESLint rules
- [packages/prettier-config](mdc:packages/prettier-config) - Code formatting
- [packages/tsconfig](mdc:packages/tsconfig) - TypeScript configurations
- [packages/mdx-plugins](mdc:packages/mdx-plugins) - MDX transformations

## Key Directories in Web App

### Source Structure ([apps/web/src](mdc:apps/web/src))

- `app/[locale]/` - Internationalized routes
- `components/` - React components organized by feature
- `orpc/routers/` - API endpoints
- `content/` - MDX content for blog/projects/pages
- `lib/` - Core utilities and configurations
- `hooks/` - Custom React hooks
- `store/` - Zustand state management

### Content Structure

- [apps/web/src/content/blog](mdc:apps/web/src/content/blog) - Blog posts in MDX
- [apps/web/src/content/projects](mdc:apps/web/src/content/projects) - Project showcases
- [apps/web/src/content/pages](mdc:apps/web/src/content/pages) - Static pages

## Docs App Structure

- [apps/docs/src/content](mdc:apps/docs/src/content) - Documentation MDX files
- [apps/docs/src/components/demos](mdc:apps/docs/src/components/demos) - Component demos

## Configuration Files

- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json) - Turborepo pipeline configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root workspace configuration
- [.env.example](mdc:.env.example) - Environment variable template
